    "parent_block_id": "",
    "type": "paragraph",
    "text": "This guide covers the standard equipment inspection process for Cedar Ridge. All equipment must be inspected at least once per quarter.",
    "order": "1",
    "created_time": "2025-12-01T10:00:00-08:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-12-28T10:00:00-07:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "blk_003",
    "page_id": "pg_equip_guide",
    "parent_block_id": "",
    "type": "bulleted_list_item",
    "text": "Shinai: Check for cracks, splinters, loose tsukagawa. Flex test each slat.",
    "order": "2",
    "created_time": "2025-12-01T10:00:00-08:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-12-28T10:00:00-07:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "blk_004",
    "page_id": "pg_equip_guide",
    "parent_block_id": "",
    "type": "bulleted_list_item",
    "text": "Kote: Inspect palmar stitching, check padding compression, verify kote-himo ties.",
    "order": "3",
    "created_time": "2025-12-01T10:00:00-08:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-12-28T10:00:00-07:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": ""
  },
  {
    "id": "blk_005",
    "page_id": "pg_equip_guide",
    "parent_block_id": "",
    "type": "bulleted_list_item",
    "text": "Bogu: Check men-gane for cracks, verify do straps, inspect tare for fraying.",
    "order": "4",
    "created_time": "2025-12-01T10:00:00-08:00",
    "last_edited_time": "2026-12-28T10:00:00-07:00",
    "has_children": "false",
    "checked": ""
  },
  {
